description:
Spacious and modern two-bedroom, two-bathroom bi-level apartment with private balcony and rooftop deck in Center City’s Washington Square West. ALL UTILITIES INCLUDED. $2,895.00
 Private Balcony and Rooftop Deck featuring Southern Views;
 Hardwood floors throughout;
 Floor-to-ceiling windows;
 Recessed Lighting;
 Spiral stairs to second-floor bedroom and bathroom;
 Fully equipped kitchen with solid wood shaker cabinetry, stainless steel appliances, custom granite countertops, and breakfast bar;
 Great closet space;
 Ceramic tile bathroom w/full size tub, with designer mirror and upscale lighting;
 Washer/Dryer in unit;
 Central air/gas heat/hot water/cooking;
 Intercom/door release admittance system;
 Free extra storage.
The Carriage House Apartments is among Center City’s most sought-after addresses and is right in the heart of historic upscale Washington Square West. A mid-rise elevator building, The Carriage House features a charming and welcoming central lobby that is a warm inviting place to come home to.
Easy walk to a wide variety of shopping, restaurants, and sites, including Acme market, Whole Foods, Starbucks, The Magic Garden as well as Walnut, Market, and South Street shopping and dining.
Just steps away are the medical and educational facilities of Jefferson, University of Pennsylvania, Wills Eye, Pennsylvania Hospitals, University of the Arts, Temple, and Avenue of the Arts theaters.
Close Public Transportation, including buses, subway, and Patco lines. Plenty of off-street parking options are available.
